Innovate Guildford 2019: Science and Arts Festival Innovate Guildford 2019 takes place on Saturday 23 March from 10am to 5pm at G Live in Guildford. Join us for a fun and inspiring family festival celebrating the interlinked worlds of science and the arts. The theme for our 2019 festival is Future Living. Don't miss this chance to peek into the future and give your brain a great day out! With amazing exhibits, interactive activities, workshops and talks, Innovate Guildford is FREE to attend and packed with entertainment.This fascinating festival has something for everyone! Young and old will be thrilled and intrigued by the exciting displays on offer. Take a look at our video and visit the Innovate Guildford page to find out more.
